snippet.title: World War Z - PvPvZ Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a look at the variety of competitive PvPvZ modes in which players will face off against the living and the dead. World War Z will be released in 2019 for PS4, Xbox One, and PC via the Epic Games Store.

World War Z Gameplay Showcase - Gamescom 2018:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NnSBAaD-io4

World War Z - Introducing: The Horde Trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mCEpIjzwAy4

Subscribe to IGN for more!
http://www.youtube.com/user/IGNentertainment?sub_confirmation=1
